{
  "stem": "11882.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got a new editor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Our dear boss left us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Probably, he went to Spain.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Probably we were trying to influence Spain, too, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And probably because he would either have to go to the army or go to South Amer-- or Spain.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He went away, and we got someone that wasn't so kind to me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "At any rate, it didn't seem that way to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had an editor that changed Goebbels words, and I didn't like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Goebbels had said-- he-- Goebbels quoted the Bible or quoted God.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He said, be either hot or cold.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "For if ye are lukewarm, I will spit ye out of my mouth.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Goebbels [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Quoting the Bible, as Goebbels often did, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And this editor changed my lukewarm to tepid, which is a silly word, in my opinion.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "If you look at it in the dictionary, you might find it as a synonym.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But I didn't like my lukewarm-- I fought for my lukewarm, and that cost me my job.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I got too 'why should I.' But Goebbels did say, lukewarm.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I've gone all through the Bible, I don't know how many times in my childhood.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And in the English version of the Old Testament, Goebbels-- or not Goebbels.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Goebbels wasn't in the Old Testament, at least.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But he-- they-- they said, I will spit ye out of my mouth if you're not hot or cold, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Be-- be something, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he changed the lukewarm into tepid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I felt pretty bitter about myself that I had, you know, had a bad temper.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyhow, and I sat in Jackson Park, and I felt very bad.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had given-- I needed the job, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
